  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in the tandoor clay pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the sliced zucchini and cook until it is tender.",
    "Add the curry powder, turmeric, cumin, salt, and black pepper, and stir well.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh cilantro.",
    "Use a thermometer to ensure the temperature reaches 165 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Let it rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
    "Garnish with fresh herbs, such as parsley or cilantro."
